Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.99,0:00:23.50,Start,,0,0,0,,{\fad(780,644)\be1\pos(174,295)}Long ago, when the Earth was young,\NDemonkind ruled the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:33.51,Start,,0,0,0,,{\fad(775,644)\be1\pos(157,288)}Over time, the surface of the Earth\Nwas overrun by a new dominant race.\NThe former masters of Earth hid\Nin the uncharted recesses of the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:42.52,Start,,0,0,0,,{\fad(775,644)\be1\pos(118,280)}However, demons are capable of living\Nfor tens of thousands of years...\NThey have begun to scour the planet,\Ntaking it back for their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.06,0:00:49.52,Start,,0,0,0,,{\fad(775,644)\be1\pos(162,275)}We now embrace our life with fear,\Nday by day, crawling toward oblivion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.08,0:01:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The mic is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.68,0:01:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,2 minutes before we're on the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.55,0:01:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, all of us are truly in your debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.81,0:01:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.50,0:01:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It is I who should thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.65,0:01:47.33,Notes,,0,0,0,,Signs: TAKE BACK JAPAN\NKILL EVERY DEVILMAN
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.72,0:02:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How cute, nice and ripe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.63,0:02:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time since\NI've tasted human flesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.13,0:03:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't eat just one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.64,0:03:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a Devilman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.26,0:03:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, how do you like my venom?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.57,0:03:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job, Yumi!\NExactly as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.93,0:03:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's getting more and more dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Demons are taking on\Nhuman form more often every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost like something big is about to—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Miko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You jerk! Let her—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.56,0:05:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother fu—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you stand up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And you Yumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.99,0:05:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a demon...\NI'm not a demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.25,0:06:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, jackass!\NYou know how to drive or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.07,0:06:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell's wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Shaddap'!\NI bet you're a demon, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I most certainly am not...\NSir, stop! Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You lying demon bitch!\NI'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.46,0:06:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Tare-chan, has Akira-kun called?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:06:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.28,0:07:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been 3 days now.\NWhat could be keeping him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.62,0:07:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You must miss your lover boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.60,0:07:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So where's Dad, and everybody else?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.14,0:07:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He said they went demon hunting...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Satou-san, over in Sanchou-me.\NI said I wouldn't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But you have to go!\NIf you don't, they'll say we're traitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.42,0:07:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It was about that time I found my father's notes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.87,0:07:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryou?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.39,0:07:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,From them, I learned the awful truth about demons...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.68,0:07:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And even the supposed 'Devilman'.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:08:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What you are about to see is shocking\Nfootage given to us by Asuka Ryou.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.14,0:08:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Fudou Akira.\NHe was my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.76,0:09:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Akira, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.98,0:09:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister, sister!\NSister, this is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.70,0:09:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Akira's in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.88,0:09:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister, sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.74,0:09:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.57,0:10:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Tare-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.91,0:10:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Tare-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.39,0:10:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad? Mum?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.77,0:11:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Tare... chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We must unite to find these demons now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They are clever and transform, taking the shapes of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.51,0:11:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There are likely demons among you\Nand you don't even realise it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.68,0:11:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I know you're really human?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That stupid TV broadcast, it's making everyone riot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.17,0:12:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Miko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.78,0:12:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried about Makimura Miki and her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.62,0:12:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll meet up with you two later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.96,0:12:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Rendezvous with the Devilman Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.46,0:13:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We got that witch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.29,0:15:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, we're gonna' be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.03,0:15:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki-chan, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.11,0:15:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.09,0:16:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.24,0:16:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The Devilman Army scout troops are\Ncombating a squadron of demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.56,0:16:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The one named Selos seems to be their leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Selos...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood. Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.29,0:16:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.94,0:16:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, wait a minute! Akira-sama,\Nare you sure you're up for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.37,0:16:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?\NI'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They followed Yumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Devilman, Fudou Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.06,0:17:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If you pledge your loyalty to my own\NDemon Army, I'll spare your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.18,0:17:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll it be, Fudou Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.69,0:17:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Fudou Akira, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.03,0:17:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Satan-sama,\Nyour plan is working marvellously!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.04,0:17:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.41,0:17:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,As I knew it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.44,0:18:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.95,0:18:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything begins, here and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.64,0:18:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.27,0:18:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.80,0:18:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.86,0:19:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.80,0:19:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.90,0:19:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Demonkind's greatest hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.68,0:19:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Amon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.86,0:19:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna' slaughter that creepy son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.08,0:19:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I'll destroy him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:19:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.82,0:20:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa... he's strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't beat this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.61,0:21:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck! FUCK!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.47,0:22:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Selos-sama! Amon—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.62,0:22:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You ran from an enemy!\NTotally unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.16,0:22:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So that'd make us enemies?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.32,0:22:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got just one question...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.47,0:22:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Satan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.23,0:22:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Amon... I'd love to fight with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.89,0:23:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're known as the ultimate hero of all Demonkind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.17,0:23:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,At last, the time has come\Nto defeat you with my own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.97,0:23:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll mean so much more...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.44,0:23:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you've taken your body\Nback from that human Fudou Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.39,0:23:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Where, is, Satan?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.04,0:23:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.38,0:23:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find him after I've dealt with your sorry ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.85,0:23:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it. I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.05,0:23:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn them...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.49,0:23:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.67,0:24:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what he's like...\NYou're a hero all right, Amon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.42,0:24:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like there's still some fight in you after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.11,0:24:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to win this.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.77,0:25:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.96,0:26:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Been a long time, Satan!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.57,0:26:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I was trapped, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.05,0:27:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside that wretched human,\NFudou Akira, to fight for Mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.51,0:27:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You used me, hiding me inside that worthless human's body!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.98,0:27:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,All my shame, and my fury...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.22,0:27:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a taste of it yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.20,0:27:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Amon, you mean you don't know yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.09,0:27:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I suppose you couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.15,0:27:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Fudou Akira isn't dead, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.81,0:27:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.84,0:27:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,AWAKEN, AKIRA!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.39,0:27:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.57,0:27:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so spaced out?\NYou're weird, Akira-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.00,0:27:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.08,0:28:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you thinking about that story I told you earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.23,0:28:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what do you think I should do?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.76,0:28:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, Miki-chan is such a pain.\NBut I'm still worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.39,0:28:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.90,0:28:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... what were we talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.64,0:28:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You really weren't listening! Pfft...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.81,0:28:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.34,0:28:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki-chan! Miki I—
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.30,0:28:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.07,0:28:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.66,0:28:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki, it's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.57,0:28:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,MIKI!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.07,0:29:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't you just leave me be?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.80,0:29:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we're not through yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.79,0:29:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.34,0:29:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Been looking for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.72,0:29:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Why show this to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.82,0:29:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to fight me.\NThis time, winner controls all!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.46,0:29:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If a fight is all you want, you're gonna' fucking get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.98,0:33:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I... going to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.96,0:33:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.56,0:33:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.70,0:33:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.91,0:33:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.59,0:33:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.36,0:34:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done nothing but make Makimura Miki suffer...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.10,0:34:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fault you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.77,0:34:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I... killed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.91,0:34:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.30,0:35:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.37,0:35:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you... crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.50,0:35:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Over a woman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.53,0:35:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you even have the strength to stand up?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.12,0:35:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd thought...\NI could never be human again...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.82,0:35:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But I never let go of my human heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.20,0:35:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You could never understand how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.09,0:35:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be defeated by you!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.18,0:36:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.67,0:36:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for the final blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.46,0:36:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.66,0:36:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.39,0:37:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
